VAR swap_value = SELECTEDVALUE('Formula Swap'[Value]) // Gets the value of the Formula Swap

VAR fy = IF( ISBLANK(SELECTEDVALUE('_Fiscal Years'[FY])), BLANK(), SELECTEDVALUE('_Fiscal Years'[FY]) - 1)  // The Previous FY
VAR amount = // using the date table filtering from a slicer as the relationship used.  Without specifying, the Billing Decision View Sheet Date will be used.
SWITCH(swap_value,
    2, CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units_billable]), USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])),  // Billable units 
    3, CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units_nonbillable]), USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])),  // Nonbillable units 
    4, CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units_admin]), USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])),  // Admin units
CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units]), USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])))  // Total units 
VAR amount_prev = // Calculates the amount that occured in the previous FY
SWITCH(swap_value,
    2, CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units_billable]), _Dates[FY] = fy, USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])),  // Billable units 
    3, CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units_nonbillable]), _Dates[FY] = fy, USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])),  // Nonbillable units 
    4, CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units_admin]), _Dates[FY] = fy, USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])),  // Admin units 
CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units]), _Dates[FY] = fy, USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])))  // Total units 
VAR diff_amount = amount - amount_prev  // Finds the difference
RETURN
